thread.title: Congress Leery of Trump’s Cuts to Children’s Health Program

author: Kristina Peterson
title: Congress Leery of Trump’s Cuts to Children’s Health Program

organizations.name: congress leery of trump’s cuts to children’s health program

text:
WASHINGTON—President Donald Trump’s proposal to roll back $7 billion from the popular Children’s Health Insurance Program drew immediate bipartisan concern Tuesday, an indication of the hurdles the effort to cut federal spending will face in the Senate.
The proposed cuts to the children’s health program quickly emerged as the most contentious element of Mr. Trump’s request that Congress rescind about $15 billion in funds that had been previously authorized but not spent.
